---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Mark Wylde" currentPage="about">
	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>About Me</h2>
			<div class="about-content">
				<div class="about-text">
					<p>
						Hello! I'm Mark Wylde, a web developer passionate about building simple, efficient solutions.
						I believe in the philosophy of "You Ain't Gonna Need It" (YAGNI) and enjoy working on projects
						that solve real problems without unnecessary complexity.
					</p>
					<p>
						My journey into web development began with a love for creating things that work well and are
						easy to understand. Since then, I've honed my skills in JavaScript, Node.js, and various web
						technologies. I'm always eager to learn new things and explore innovative solutions.
					</p>

					<h3>My Approach</h3>
					<p>
						I believe great software comes from understanding both the technical challenges
						and the human needs behind them. Whether I'm writing code, reviewing architecture,
						or working with a team, I always ask: "How can we make this simpler and better?"
					</p>

					<h3>What I Focus On</h3>
					<ul class="focus-list">
						<li>Building web applications with modern JavaScript</li>
						<li>Creating simple, maintainable backend systems</li>
						<li>Open source contributions and community building</li>
						<li>Sharing knowledge through writing and speaking</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="contact-section">
					<div class="avatar-container">
						<img src="/src/assets/avatar-juggle.png" alt="Mark Wylde Avatar" class="avatar" />
					</div>
					<h3>Get In Touch</h3>
					<p>
						I'm always open to discussing new projects, creative ideas, or opportunities to be part of something great.
						Feel free to reach out!
					</p>
					<div class="contact-methods">
						<a href="mailto:mark@wylde.net">Email Me</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/markwylde" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
						<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mwylde" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.avatar-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.avatar {
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 15px var(--shadow-color);
	}

	.about-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.about-text h3 {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.focus-list {
		margin-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.focus-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.contact-section {
		background-color: var(--secondary-bg);
		padding: 25px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 15px var(--shadow-color);
		border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		height: fit-content;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 10px;
		margin-top: 15px;
	}

	.contact-methods a {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		padding: 10px 20px;
		border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		border-radius: 5px;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.contact-methods a:hover {
		background-color: var(--accent-color);
		color: var(--secondary-bg);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 30px;
		}
	}
</style>
